Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.11,0:24:48.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Balsa decides to\Ntake drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.12,0:24:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, "Soil and Heroes."
